"ensure that the application has deleted all fonts using "
":cpp:func:`lv_font_manager_delete_font`.  The font manager will check the"
" reference status of all allocated fonts.  If there are still fonts being"
" referenced, the font manager will fail to be destroyed and the function "
"will return false."
